Run an rpp node

Usage: chain-cli <COMMAND>

Commands:
  node      Run the node runtime
  wallet    Run the wallet runtime
  hybrid    Run the hybrid runtime (node + wallet)
  validator Validator runtime and tooling
  help      Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help     Print help
  -V, --version  Print version

Exit codes:
  0 - runtime exited cleanly
  2 - configuration validation failed
  3 - runtime startup failed
  4 - unexpected runtime error

Cleanup runbook: docs/mempool_cleanup.md
